column5: Anybody have some info about Burwell or Stanley area?  Tx!!!
I use port Bruce all summer. Straight out from the creek to about 40 feet. Depending in wind and direction many good days
ya I know that, but how about this late in the fall? I've never been out in November
Try the 60 foot range.  If you have sonar, you will find the schools.  Bring minnows!
